French's quote (') are blocking the injections of parameters (exemple in activity stream) :
{code:java}
changé létat à {1} sur {2}
{code}
Same problème in the About page where all the quotes are missings.
{code:java}
Lutilisation de ce produit est ...
{code}
Or in the admin menu : "Recherche dans ladministration" or "Accès à lapplication"

I think it is related to message properties bundles where quotes are used has escaped caracters and needs to be doubled otherwise.

